reviews.review_text: Best sounding source. A very good show.  In the top half dozen for the tour.  A very good sounding, obviously fob recording.  I always thought the acoustics at Capital Center were pretty decent for a bigger arena.   There are a couple other good sources for this show, but I think this one sounds the best.
